    "title": "Immediate Requirement Production Engineer at Havells India",
    "description": "We at Havells India are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Varanasi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Havells India:\nHavells India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in 5S\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Havells India!",
